    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>The 12 boxes contain files of Hardy Cross Dillard's work as
         judge on the International Court of Justice from 1970 to 1979.
         Significant materials besides the case files include 20
         folders of personal correspondence, speeches and writings.</p>
    </scopecontent>
